                  Iacob ſaw a Ladder reaching to heauen;
                     Gen. 28.12. Chriſt with Angells on the Ladder going vp

and downe: God aboue it, promiſing two things. Firſt, to bee his God, and bring him backe againe. Secondly, to giue him that ſame Land of Canaan that hee promiſed to his Fathers, Abraham and Iſaac, &c.
